prefix_hash, hash_linkedlist, vector 三种 memtable 不支持并发写入，
需自动设置 allow_concurrent_memtable_write=false。

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 .../site/ycsb/db/rocksdb/RocksDBClient.java   | 28 +++++++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 28 insertions(+)

diff --git a/rocksdb/src/main/java/site/ycsb/db/rocksdb/RocksDBClient.java b/rocksdb/src/main/java/site/ycsb/db/rocksdb/RocksDBClient.java
